snippet.title: ETimes
snippet.description:
BOMBAY TIMES IS NOW A PART OF ETIMES.

This is an official YouTube channel of ETimes which is a Times of India Group property. It covers Bollywood, Regional movies, TV, Life & Style, Fashion and Celebrity news.

With 110 Mn+ Users and 900 Mn+ Page views, ETimes features video content from Bombay Times, Delhi Times, Chennai Times, Hyderabad Times, Bangalore Times, Pune Times, Calcutta Times etc. It is the Entertainment channel of Times of India website. 

Here is the link to our official website: http://www.etimes.in
